answer:
Immunization schedules vary between countries. It is important to keep all immunization records and follow the recommended immunization schedule, whether in Canada or Hong Kong. Bring your Canadian immunization records to health appointments so the health care provider knows which vaccines your baby has already received.
Immunization Nurse
